3.1  Resolved Resonances <125 eV                                  4040 1451
--------------------------------                                  4040 1451
                                                                  4040 1451
   This evaluation contains no resolved resonance parameters.     4040 1451
Instead, below 125 eV, the capture and elastic scattering cross   4040 1451
sections were assumed to be in 1/v form and constant,             4040 1451
respectively. The capture cross section at 0.0253 eV was          4040 1451
determined by the systematics from the neighboring Zr isotopes.   4040 1451
The scattering cross section was calculated from R = 6.737 fm.    4040 1451
