3.2  Unresolved Resonance Region : 125 ev - 100 keV               4040 1451
---------------------------------------------------               4040 1451
                                                                  4040 1451
    Unresolved resonance parameters were adopted from JENDL-2.    4040 1451
The neutron strength functions, S0, S1 and S2 were calculated     4040 1451
with optical model code casthy[5]. The observed level spacing     4040 1451
was determined to reproduce the capture cross section calculated  4040 1451
with casthy. The effective scattering radius was obtained from    4040 1451
fitting to the calculated total cross section at 100 keV.         4040 1451
